{"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"roleHeading":"Class","symbolKind":"class","externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B34ThemeSwitchComponentTokensProviderC","title":"OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider"}]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of switch"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"switch \/ toggle"}]},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSSwitch"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"code":"AllSwitchComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"code":"SwitchComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"switch \/ toggle"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Switch"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of colors (from "},{"code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"spaces (from "},{"code":"AllSpacesSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":") ,  dimensions ("},{"code":"AllDimensionSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"sizes ("},{"code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"), borders ("},{"code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":") and opacities ("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllOpacitiySemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider"},"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/AllSwitchComponentTokensProvider","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/19OUDSTokensComponent06SwitchB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s8CopyableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s9EscapableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/TokensProvider"],"kind":"relationships","type":"conformsTo"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemeswitchcomponenttokensprovider"]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":